{
  "texts": [
    "What are the implications of the use of ChatGPT for PL based on current Chat-GPT technologies? 3.",
    "How do students perceive the effectiveness and usefulness of ChatGPT in facilitating their PL experience?",
    "A total of 51 postgraduate participants were recruited to participate in the study.",
    "These participants were enrolled in an Educational Reform and Development in Global Context class at the Education University of Hong Kong and learned about education reform concepts.",
    "The conversations of all the students with the tutor bot are collected and analyzed qualitatively."
  ]
}